    <section id="projects" class="mb-5">
      <h2>Key Projects</h2>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>HMM Regime Forecasting System:</strong> Predicts bull/bear market states using probability models and market indicators for data-driven investment insights.</li>
        <li><strong>IoT Intrusion Detection:</strong> End-to-end ML system for analyzing and detecting network intrusions in IoT systems using machine learning and feature engineering.</li>
        <li><strong>Regime Dynamics Simulator:</strong> Simulated financial regimes using Hidden Markov Models and the Law of Large Numbers to study convergence behaviour in stochastic systems.</li>
